Transmutation
Levels: Ranger 2
Components: V
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: 1d4 + 1 rounds

This spell functions like the haste spell but only affects the caster. In addition, you gain a +4 dodge AC bonus for 6 seconds after casting the spell.

<i>Two quick syllables release the power of the spell, and the world moves a bit slower about you.</i>